r with a weapon or unarmed.<br><br>Examples: throw Melee Combat/STR 8+ to hit a target with a sword. The Combat chapter has more detailed examples of how to use the Melee Combat skill.","shortdescr":"Fighting hand-to-hand, either with a weapon or unarmed","subtype":"","key":"key","difficulty":"Average","rolltype":"Normal","trainingNotes":"","reference":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"GOmBKof9PfoHZ54T":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_3btd7dw9pac","path":"Cepheus Deluxe - Items#/CF_SEP/Skills","color":"#00aaaa"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.twodsix.cepheus-light-items.eVVFG5oHgsBycy1K"}},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}},{"_id":"7sSLTA8unq9OEgDc","name":"Stealth","type":"skills","img":"./systems/twodsix/assets/icons/stealth.svg","system":{"docReference":"","pdfReference":{"type":"","href":"","label":""},"value":1,"characteristic":"DEX","type":"skills","description":"Stealth: the ability to be unseen and unheard, both while stationary and moving.<br><br>Examples: sneaking past a guard is an Opposed throw where the interloper throws Stealth/DEX while the guard throws Recon/INT, or Stealth/INT, whichever is better. Throw Stealth/DEX 8+ to hide from searchlights. Throw Stealth/END 8+ if the character has to hide and stay motionless for long periods. Bypassing more advanced sensors and security systems require specialized equipment and impose higher Target Numbers. Characters without Stealth or Recon roll to spot interlopers unskilled.","shortdescr":"Training in being unseen and unheard","subtype":"","key":"key","difficulty":"Average","rolltype":"Normal","trainingNotes":"","reference":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"GOmBKof9PfoHZ54T":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_3btd7dw9pac","path":"Cepheus Deluxe - Items#/CF_SEP/Skills","color":"#00aaaa"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.twodsix.cepheus-light-items.Vhk7ymYo5sn4HVYZ"}},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}},{"_id":"mhZ1sFq0L3gre678","name":"Gun Combat","type":"skills","img":"./systems/twodsix/assets/icons/gun-combat.svg","system":{"docReference":"","pdfReference":{"type":"","href":"","label":""},"value":1,"characteristic":"DEX","type":"skills","description":"Gun Combat: using small arms, crossbows, and bows in combat.<br><br>Examples: throw Gun Combat/DEX 8+ to hit a target in Effective range with a handgun. Throw Gun combat/DEX 10+ to hit a target at Maximum range. See the Combat chapter for more information.","shortdescr":"Using small arms, crossbows, and bows in combat","subtype":"","key":"key","difficulty":"Average","rolltype":"Normal","trainingNotes":"","reference":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"GOmBKof9PfoHZ54T":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_3btd7dw9pac","path":"Cepheus Deluxe - Items#/CF_SEP/Skills","color":"#00aaaa"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.twodsix.cepheus-light-items.enQOAVdQXndSdf0j"}},"_stats":{"systemId":null,"systemVersion":null,"coreVersion":null,"createdTime":null,"modifiedTime":null,"lastModifiedBy":null}},{"_id":"BnY1C1wWkn9FuEvp","name":"Athletics","type":"skills","img":"./systems/twodsix/assets/icons/athletics-dexterity.svg","system":{"docReference":"","pdfReference":{"type":"","href":"","label":""},"value":1,"characteristic":"END","type":"skills","description":"Athletics: the ability to exert oneself physically. You may add the Athletics skill to appropriate physical characteristic rolls. This skill is never rolled unskilled.<br><br>Examples: throw Athletics/END 6+ to swim against a powerful current. To move past obstacles while running, using Parkour-style moves, throw Athletics/DEX 8+. To climb a rope quickly, throw Athletics/STR 8+.","shortdescr":"The ability to exert oneself physically","subtype":"","key":"key","difficulty":"Average","rolltype":"Normal","trainingNotes":"","r